OL,3,C'Showstopper' peacock voted Britain's
OL,4,Cfavourite butterfly
OL,6,FThe colourful peacock has fluttered to
OL,7,Fthe top spot in a poll to reveal the
OL,8,Fnation's favourite butterfly.
OL,10,FPeacock butterflies, with their
OL,11,Fstriking colours and "eye-spots"
OL,12,Fdesigned to fend off predators, beat
OL,13,F59 other British species in the vote
OL,14,Frun by Butterfly Conservation.
OL,16,FMore than 20,000 votes were cast
OL,17,Facross the UK, with a rainbow of
OL,18,Fcolourful species making up the top
OL,19,Ffive, the conservationists said.
OL,26,@sD@VOUsD@`O]
