OL,3,C'Showstopper' peacock voted Britain's
OL,4,Cfavourite butterfly
OL,6,FThe orange-tip butterfly came a close
OL,7,Fsecond to the peacock, followed by red
OL,8,Fadmirals in third, holly blues in
OL,9,Ffourth and the bright yellow brimstone
OL,10,Fbutterfly in fifth.
OL,12,FThe charity, which declared a
OL,13,F"butterfly emergency" in 2024 as
OL,14,Fnumbers recorded during its annual Big
OL,15,FButterfly Count fell to a record low,
OL,16,Fis now calling on everyone to take
OL,17,Fpart in this year's count to help
OL,18,Fscientists get an updated picture of
OL,19,Fhow Britain's most common butterflies
OL,20,Fare faring.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@UO]
