OL,3,C'Showstopper' peacock voted Britain's
OL,4,Cfavourite butterfly
OL,6,FButterfly Conservation's head of
OL,7,Fengagement, Kate Merry, said: "The
OL,8,Fresponse to Britain's Favourite
OL,9,FButterfly has been absolutely
OL,10,Fwonderful, and we're not surprised.
OL,12,F"It's clear that people up and down
OL,13,Fthe country love butterflies of all
OL,14,Fshapes, sizes and colours, and voted
OL,15,Fin their thousands for their
OL,16,Ffavourites."
OL,18,FBut she said: "The peacock is a worthy
OL,19,Fwinner, it's a true showstopper and a
OL,20,Fspecies that I bet a lot of us picture
OL,21,Fwhen we think of butterflies.
OL,26,@oD@_OUtD@AOUxD@LO]zD@OOU
