OL,3,C'Showstopper' peacock voted Britain's
OL,4,Cfavourite butterfly
OL,6,FPeacock butterflies are regular
OL,7,Fvisitors to gardens and green spaces
OL,8,Facross the whole of the UK,
OL,9,Fparticularly where there are patches
OL,10,Fof nettles as the plants are their
OL,11,Fcaterpillars' favourite food,
OL,12,FButterfly Conservation said.
OL,14,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
